CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 18, 1958, page 19, reads: "Bandleader - Pittsburgh bandleader Walt Harper, right, receives a scroll from the University of Pittsburgh's Phi Epsilon Pi Fraternity in recognition of his contribution to jazz in Pittsburgh area. Making the presentation is Raven Garfinkel, fraternity social chairman. Harper also is an honorary member of the frat. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Raven Garfinkel, University of Pittsburgh Phi Epsilon Pi fraternity social chairman, presenting scroll to Walt Harper, standing in interior with piano
